<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link144225" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=144225&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F338724-the-emperor-of-maladies-was-well-written%2Fanswers%2F144225-i-ve-read-other-long">flag</a>
