        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/9667124-the-emperor-of-all-maladies">review of another edition</a>


          <div>
    <span class="greyText">Recommended to Riku by: </span>
      <a href="/user/show/5813283-rohini">Rohini</a>
  </div>


          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1651956-riku-sayuj?shelf=science-gen">science-gen</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1651956-riku-sayuj?shelf=r-r-rs">r-r-rs</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1651956-riku-sayuj?shelf=favorites">favorites</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1651956-riku-sayuj?shelf=cancer">cancer</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1651956-riku-sayuj?shelf=medicine">medicine</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1651956-riku-sayuj?shelf=history">history</a>
