<li class='cover' id='bookCover_20696006'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/20696006-being-mortal"><img alt="Being Mortal: Medicine and What Matters in the End" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1408324949l/20696006._SX98_.jpg" />
